text: Got a large pepperoni with butter cheese crust and a 2 liter Pepsi to share with 2 other people. Hot and fresh pizza. Pepperoni was crispy. Dough was crisp outside yet soft inside. Sauce was on point. Friendly staff. Love this pizza. It's a must have.

text: I've been going here for a while for carry out and delivery and the food and service are always good! It's hard to get that kind of consistency at a business nowadays.
